      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it drives as smooth as silk. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found your match. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 43500.0,
