    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This JZA80 Supra Turbo is a textbook example of Japanese over-engineering, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant with its sequential twin-turbocharger setup intact and functioning flawlessly. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, positive engagement, feeding power through the factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Every suspension bushing remains compliant, and the four-piston front calipers retain their original finish with zero thermal discoloration. This chassis shows no signs of torsional fatigue, and the undercarriage is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation. A true turnkey investment for the discerning collector who demands mechanical purity and matching-numbers authenticity.",
